TITLE: Invalid Code Error Response
DESCRIPTION: This Javascript snippet shows the error response when the code parameter in the token exchange request is invalid. This response indicates an issue with the authorization code provided during the token exchange process. It is crucial to handle this error to guide users toward proper authorization.
SOURCE: https://github.com/raindropio/developer-site/blob/master/v1/authentication/token.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
{"error": "bad_authorization_code"}
```

