TITLE: Successful Token Refresh Response
DESCRIPTION: This Javascript snippet shows the format of the response to a successful token refresh request. It contains new access and refresh tokens, updated expiration timestamps (milliseconds and seconds), and the token type. The expires field is deprecated; use expires_in instead.
SOURCE: https://github.com/raindropio/developer-site/blob/master/v1/authentication/token.md#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
{
  "access_token": "ae261404-18r4-47c0-bce3-e18a423da898",
  "refresh_token": "c8080368-fad2-4a9f-b2c9-73d3z850111b",
  "expires": 1209599768, //in miliseconds, deprecated
  "expires_in": 1209599, //in seconds, use this instead!!!
  "token_type": "Bearer"
}
```

