TITLE: CORS Response Headers
DESCRIPTION: Example of the HTTP response headers for CORS support. Includes Access-Control-Allow-Origin, Access-Control-Expose-Headers, and Access-Control-Allow-Credentials.
SOURCE: https://github.com/raindropio/developer-site/blob/master/README.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: http
CODE:
```
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Access-Control-Allow-Origin: http://example.com
Access-Control-Expose-Headers: ETag, Content-Type, Accept, X-RateLimit-Limit, X-RateLimit-Remaining, X-RateLimit-Reset
Access-Control-Allow-Credentials: true
```
